{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_02_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……私は冥界のナース、亡者達よ\n刮目しなさい",
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.333333333334,
          "startTime": 5.733333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……それ\nさっき俺が苦し紛れに言った設定だ……",
      "startTime": 9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "今から、貴方達は私の下僕\n私の歌と踊りに酔いしれるのよ",
      "startTime": 15.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そして、ひれ伏すがいいわ……！",
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、ミュージックスタート！",
      "startTime": 22.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "最初は戸惑ってたけど、うまくいってよかった\nていうか、莉央さんの女王様キャラ、ハマってるな……",
      "startTime": 32,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.33333333333,
          "startTime": 36.93333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま。ファンのみんなは大喜びよ\nどう？　私はコスプレだって完璧でしょ？",
      "startTime": 43.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。莉央さんが周囲に合わせるんじゃなくて\n周囲が莉央さんに合わせてしまう。圧倒的な存在感だ",
      "startTime": 50.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "私のこと、まだ分かってなかったのね\n貴方も治療してあげるわ",
      "startTime": 59.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_occult-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 38
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら？",
      "startTime": 64.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "わっ、びっくりするなぁ……\n案外終わってみればノリノリじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 69.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "うるさいわね、バカにするなら\n本当に冥界のナースの下僕にするわよ",
      "startTime": 75.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは勘弁してください……",
      "startTime": 78.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "もう、私の仕事の幅は狭いなんて\n言わせないわよ",
      "startTime": 83.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "どんな仕事だって、私は、神崎莉央は\n観客を圧倒してみせるんだから――",
      "startTime": 89.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_encore-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8433.333333333338,
          "startTime": 93.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "……そろそろアンコールの時間ね。行ってくるわ\n貴方はそこで、私のステージを見守っていなさい",
      "startTime": 100.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……本当は分かってたよ。いや、信じてたよ、莉央さん\nどんな状況でも最後にはみんなを魅了するだろうなって",
      "startTime": 110.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 500,
          "startTime": 104.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ハッピーハロウィン！",
      "startTime": 118.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6666666666572,
          "startTime": 119.36666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "『神崎莉央、ハロウィンイベントで新境地』\n『ソロデビュー間近か？』",
      "startTime": 128.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ニュースサイトのトップに\n今朝これが載ってた時は、さすがに驚きましたよ",
      "startTime": 132.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "思った以上に盛り上がったわね\nアンコールに二回も応えちゃったわ",
      "startTime": 138.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "予想以上の結果だな……\n莉央さんはやっぱり凄いですね",
      "startTime": 144.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、愛やこころより仕事の幅が狭いって\n言ってたくせに",
      "startTime": 150.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、あれは向き不向きを言っただけで……\nでも、余計な心配だと今回の仕事で分かりました",
      "startTime": 156.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんは、天性のスターですね\nで、どうします？　ソロデビューに興味はあります？",
      "startTime": 164.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ないわよ\n少なくともLizNoirを続けている間はね",
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "私の目標はLizNoirがアイドルの頂点に立つこと\n今はそれ以外のことに興味ないの",
      "startTime": 179.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "聞くまでもなかったですね",
      "startTime": 181.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、たまにならこんな仕事もいいかもね\n新鮮な喜びがあったわ",
      "startTime": 187.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-koh013.m4a",
